title: Click...Nothing
body: I cannot Launch League at all!!!!!!!!!

replies.body: I can help with this!  Firstly, give your PC a restart in case something has crashed in the background.  Otherwise, your OS settings could be blocking your patcher from launching so nothing is coming up.  You'll want to go through the steps found in the [permissions](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) guide to resolve this.  Let me know if you have any questions!
